        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12">
                <p><br>Question No.1 今の気持ちは？(1つ選んでください)</p>
            </div>
            <div class="answer">
            <div class="button">
            </div>
                <div class="col-6">
                    <p><%= f.radio_button :question1, "option1" %><label id="song_question1_option1" for="song_question1_option1">世の中は生きづらい</label></p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-6">
                    <p><%= f.radio_button :question1, "option2" %><label id="song_question1_option2" for="song_question1_option2">目標はあるけど一歩が踏み出せない</label></p>
                </div>
