                </div>
                <div class="col-6">
                    <p><%= f.radio_button :question1, "option4" %><label id="song_question1_option4" for="song_question1_option4">自分をとにかく奮い立たせたい</label></p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-6">
                    <p><%= f.radio_button :question1, "option5" %><label id="song_question1_option5" for="song_question1_option5">卒業シーズンにピッタリの曲が聴きたい</label></p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-6">
                    <p><%= f.radio_button :question1, "option6" %><label id="song_question1_option6" for="song_question1_option6">面白い曲、クスッと笑える曲が聴きたい</label></p>
